{
  "_note": "Synthetic placeholder frames used for unit tests. Replace raw_payload values with real Yahoo WebSocket payloads captured via Chrome DevTools once the draft room is accessible (~August). See docs/stages/stage-11-yahoo-playwright.md for capture instructions.",
